* payload cms

* why it matters
- Next.js-first fullstack framework with CMS, admin panel, db schema, auth, REST, GraphQL, and Local API in one codebase
- code-first: schema, access, hooks, custom UI, and project structure live in git
- best mental model: Payload config defines data model + admin behavior + API behavior

